615
00:32:58,719 --> 00:33:00,520
I want to do Shakespeare in this format, you know?

616
00:33:01,861 --> 00:33:06,763
But I think that will come as more spaces become interested

617
00:33:06,843 --> 00:33:08,224
in putting this sort of thing on.

618
00:33:08,644 --> 00:33:10,264
But again, this ties up with the idea

619
00:33:10,284 --> 00:33:11,685
of doing it within an escape room, where

620
00:33:11,725 --> 00:33:13,106
the more you can control the environment,

621
00:33:13,406 --> 00:33:15,467
the more that you can reflect that back to the player

622
00:33:15,967 --> 00:33:17,828
and get the player doing something specific.

623
00:33:18,048 --> 00:33:22,370
But it doesn't have to work that way if the story fits

624
00:33:22,510 --> 00:33:24,171
the environment correctly.

625
00:33:24,991 --> 00:33:25,612
Does that make sense?

626
00:33:25,812 --> 00:33:25,992
Yeah.

